cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about object tracking using RGB-Thermal data and proposes a new approach for integrating dual attention mechanisms for visual tracking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques for feature representation and attention estimation, which suggests it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with multi-modal data fusion, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and the proposed algorithm has potential applications in robotics, which could place it in cs.RO (Robotics).
